metadata.name: 서울바운드 Partner
metadata.description: The Partner Pass is for friends who supported this gathering in their own unique way. SeoulBound could not have happened without the support of our dedicated and passionate partners!
metadata.criteria:
To become a partner of SeoulBound, please contact our crew on Twitter @seoul_bound.
 
Partner Passes will be granted to a limited number of participants from partner organizations, based on their level of contribution to the gathering.
metadata.evidence: The winner of this badge is an official partner of SeoulBound 2023 and an ecosystem contributor in the DAO space who has made valuable contributions to the gathering.
